{"tid":162290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【奉勸】各位生得高嘅巴絲落雨唔好去人多嘅地方","createTime":"2017-03-19T07:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T09:46:55.000Z","uid":65467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"38ff1f3078c785ebdc55746497ba5958972f49ae","tid":162290,"uid":65467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"真係會隨時俾啲遮批撚走對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係要歧視啲生得比較矮嘅人，我亦都覺得身高唔代表啲咩<br />\n<br />\n但係遇著啲橫衝直撞嘅大媽/廢老，你身手冇番咁上下，都隨時俾佢地啲旋風遮劃破你嘅靈魂之窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,到時因為咁而變咗盲閪就真係on99<br />\n<br />\n所以奉勸各位生得高嘅巴絲落雨盡量唔好係條街搏命，或者宅係屋企算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 米八巨棍，身手好，但係都逃唔過佢地嘅魔傘，隻眼好撚痛呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nps 轉過嚟lihkg之後做咗cdrom一排，第一次開post，記得以前高登有巴打都身同感受但搵唔番個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7722ef23845858a45e3deceb06bb3217f77f3944","tid":162290,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:28:40.000Z","msg":"建議立法規定出街擔遮要先考牌<br />\n唔係一律只準著雨褸"},{"pid":"4f018c808e9ab0e372f6af71484ac2b6361c73ce","tid":162290,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:30:15.000Z","msg":"落雨戴眼罩是常識吧"},{"pid":"640be5edeab8a089324f334c57a9bdb441772247","tid":162290,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:31:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba10bfff1ce919c3e50ef17fa1de983e25f2b7ab","tid":162290,"uid":65467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議立法規定出街擔遮要先考牌<br />\n唔係一律只準著雨褸</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c39bf91184b6c7c8ed95883ec5820ed376a36358","tid":162290,"uid":65467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>建議立法規定出街擔遮要先考牌<br />\n唔係一律只準著雨褸</blockquote><br />\n<b